Package utils

Class OwnBigInteger

java.lang.Object
utils.OwnBigInteger
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<OwnBigInteger>
public class OwnBigInteger
extends Object
implements Comparable<OwnBigInteger>
This is my implementation of BigInteger. It stores the number as a digit array. The Arithmetic operations use the paper-and-pen techniques.

This implementation copies arrays using OwnArrays.arraycopy.

Note: This implemenentation only implements the operations required for this program. It does not, for example, allow for negative multiplications or square roots.
